data.title: Group photograph including Albert Edward, Prince of Wales, Princess Alexandra of Denmark on the occasion of their engagement, 1862
data.meta_description: Group photograph taken for the occasion of the engagement between Albert Edward, Prince of Wales (1841-1910), later King Edward VII to Princess Alexandra of Denmark (1843-1925), later Princess of Wales and Queen Alexandra, with members of the Princesss family including Prince Christian of Denmark (1818-1906), later Christian IX of Denmark; Princess Christian of Denmark (1817-1898); the Duke of Brabant (1835-1909), later Leopold II of Belgium; Marie Henriette of Austria, the Duchess of Brabant (1836-1902);...
